Who We Are


The global leader in cloud communications!
Founded in 1998, BroadSoft is a leading technology innovator in cloud PBX, unified communications, team collaboration and contact center solutions, designed for our service provider customers across the globe.
Acknowledged as the market share leader, our open, mobile and secure platform is trusted by 25 of the world’s top 30 service providers by revenue.




























Our Leadership
 HOME / COMPANY INFORMATION
Our leaders have seen - and shaped - change.
BroadSoft’s executive team brings cutting edge technical experience to solve service provider challenges and meet marketplace demands in the cloud communications industry.





























Our Presence


We serve customers worldwide through a global presence
Headquartered near Washington DC, BroadSoft’s growing workforce of over 1600 employees serves its global customers from more than 22 locations worldwide. 





    
 
 
 
 























Get In Touch


Get in touch to learn more about how our solutions and services can help expand your reach in the cloud communications marketplace.
