Broadsoft Launches Broadcloud Platform in Australia
May 25 17
BroadSoft introduced the BroadSoft Business BroadCloud managed cloud platform to the Australian market. Local operator Optus became the first company to adopt this platform. BroadCloud will provide Optus with a proven SaaS service delivery platform, allowing the company to deploy a UC platform for their SMB business customers with a flexible Opex service delivery model. The platform, Optus 'Loop,' is designed for Australian small and medium sized business customers.


