Welcome


Welcome to the BroadCloud Knowledge Base (KB), the fastest and easiest way to;
• Access general product information
• Access user guides and how to instruction
• Review frequently asked questions for common issues
• Review release materials and product updates









Service OVerview


BroadSoft’s BroadCloud service offers a fast and cost effective way for Service Providers to deliver Unified Communications services hosted and managed by BroadSoft - but branded, marketed and sold by our Service Provider customers. Key elements of our service include:
• BroadSoft UC Platform
• BroadSoft Cloud Network Infrastructure
• End to End Service Operating Platform












Looking for more information?  Contact your account team for details on recent and upcoming BroadCloud PBX releases, as well as additional questions you might have on the service.











